Gerresheimer Plans Acquisition in the U.S., Boersen-Zeitung Says

-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 
2011-07-01T17:39:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-01/gerresheimer-plans-acquisition-in-the-u-s-boersen-zeitung-says.html
Gerresheimer AG (GXI)  is planning a major
acquisition in the U.S. to do more business in the plastics
sector,  Boersen-Zeitung  reported today, citing Chief Financial
Officer Hans-Juergen Wiecha.  The targeted company should have annual sales of between
$100 million and $250 million, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Holger Elfes in Dusseldorf,  Germany  at 
 helfes@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Celeste Perri at   cperri@bloomberg.net . 